data.description: Welcome home! This home merges convenience with resort-style living in Eagle Harbor. Picture leisurely days by the pool, friendly tennis matches, and strolls along serene pathways. The clubhouse fosters community, while ponds offer peaceful moments. With a 1st-floor primary bedroom, 9ft ceilings, 3 spacious guest rooms, ample storage, new carpet, an updated sliding door, and a 2-car garage, this home pairs convenience with a vibrant lifestyle. The privacy fenced backyard makes a space for all in your home to enjoy. A short drive to the Peninsula over the JRB or an easy commute to North Suffolk and Downtown Smithfield, this residence embodies the perfect blend of modern living, community amenities, and accessibility. $5,000 decorating allowance offered to the new buyers.
